txt.en: You have recovered several chest of stolen dwarf-relics from the Angmarim in Tûr Ágal.\n\nThrough your efforts, the relics shall be returned to the dwarves of the Gabil'akkâ.
Collect stolen dwarf-relics in Tûr Ágal ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
You have collected many chests of stolen dwarf-relics in Tûr Ágal.
The Angmarim of Caivád Sâr have stolen countless dwarf-relics from the ruins of Elderslade and Mount Gundabad.

Chests of stolen dwarf-relics can be found in Tûr Ágal.\n\nYou have discovered chests filled with stolen dwarf-relics in Tûr Ágal. You should collect them and see that they are returned to the Gabil'akkâ.
Collect stolen dwarf-relics in Tûr Ágal ([placeholder]/[placeholder])

While exploring Tûr Ágal, the jagged tower within Caivád Sâr, you have discovered several chests filled with dwarf-relics that could only have been stolen from the ruins of Elderslade or Mount Gundabad by the Angmarim.\n\nYou should collect these chests of stolen dwarf-relics and see that they are returned to the dwarves of the Gabil'akkâ.
